## graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com
IMAPStore graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port  993
User graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass online/google.com/graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com/app/isync"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs PLAIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com
Expunge Both
Far :graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com-remote:
Near :graf.jeanclaude@gmail.com-local:
Patterns * !"Drafts" !"Junk" !"Sent" !"Trash"
Create Both
Remove None
CopyArrivalDate yes
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0

