## jegraf@ethz.ch
IMAPStore jegraf@ethz.ch-remote
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
User jegraf@ethz.ch
PassCmd "mutt_oauth2.py ~/.local/share/pass/online/ethz.ch/jegraf_OAuth_Token.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
#CertificateFile /etc/SSL/certs/ca-certificates.CRT

MaildirStore jegraf@ethz.ch-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/jegraf@ethz.ch/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/jegraf@ethz.ch/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel jegraf@ethz.ch
Expunge Both
Far :jegraf@ethz.ch-remote:
Near :jegraf@ethz.ch-local:
Patterns * !"Tasks" !"Calendar*" !"Contacts" !"Conversation History" !"Deleted Items/*" !"Notes" !"Journal" !"Outbox" !"Archive" !"Trash" !"Junk" !"Sent"
Create Both
Remove None
CopyArrivalDate yes
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0

